  "prompt": "What is the best GMAT coaching centre in Bangalore?",
  "response": "There are several reputed GMAT coaching centers in Bangalore known for their quality instruction and successful track records. Some of the top centers include:\n\n1. **Manhattan Review**: Known for its comprehensive course materials and experienced instructors, Manhattan Review offers a range of coaching options tailored to different learning needs.\n\n2. **Jamboree Education**: One of the oldest and most well-known test prep centers in India, Jamboree offers extensive classroom training and study materials designed specifically for GMAT preparation.\n\n3. **Princeton Review (Manya Education)**: Offers well-structured courses with experienced trainers, and a range of resources including practice tests, doubt-clearing sessions, and study materials.\n\n4. **TIME (Triumphant Institute of Management Education)**: Known for its extensive network and comprehensive test preparation courses, TIME offers a rigorous curriculum and practice tests that closely mimic the actual GMAT.\n\n5. **CrackVerbal**: Specializes in GMAT preparation with a focus on verbal skills, offering both online and classroom courses along with personalized study plans.\n\n6. **BYJU\u2019s Classes**: Known for its innovative teaching methods and interactive platforms, BYJU\u2019s provides both online and offline coaching options.\n\nWhen choosing a GMAT coaching center, consider factors like the duration and types of courses offered, the experience of the faculty, past student reviews, and the availability of flexible schedules or online learning if needed. It might also be beneficial to attend demo classes if available to assess the teaching quality.",
